text: Ordered kopi-siew-dai (less sugar). You will know if it’s good coffee when drink this or kopi-o. And this is very decent. Very authentic black coffee without“additives”.

Ordered Kopi Dilo Siew Dai.

Coffee tastes like 70% water, 20% sugar/milk.

Never had a worse one across hawker centres in Singapore at the moment.
A very good place for kopi in the area. The uncle is very nice and has fresh kopi all the time
